ZH: 1. 记得明天早上要去医院看病。
EN: 1. Remember to go to the hospital for a check-up tomorrow morning.

ZH: 2. 记得在去超市之前买些菜。
EN: 2. Remember to buy some groceries before going to the supermarket.

ZH: 3. 记得给爸爸打电话祝他生日快乐。
EN: 3. Remember to call dad and wish him a happy birthday.

ZH: 4. 记得在下雨天带伞出门。
EN: 4. Remember to bring an umbrella when it rains.

ZH: 5. 记得关灯后再离开房间。
EN: 5. Remember to turn off the lights before leaving the room.

ZH: 6. 记得把门锁好，不要让陌生人进来。
EN: 6. Remember to lock the door and not let strangers in.

ZH: 7. 记得在考试之前好好复习。
EN: 7. Remember to study hard before the exam.

ZH: 8. 记得今晚不要太晚睡。
EN: 8. Remember not to stay up too late tonight.

ZH: 9. 记得跟妈妈说一声再出去玩。
EN: 9. Remember to tell mom before going out to play.

ZH: 10. 记得给小狗喂食和喝水。
EN: 10. Remember to feed and water the puppy.

ZH: 11. 记得把车停在指定的停车位。
EN: 11. Remember to park the car in the designated spot.

ZH: 12. 记得在过马路时看红绿灯。
EN: 12. Remember to look at the traffic lights when crossing the street.

ZH: 13. 记得在家里穿拖鞋，不要赤脚。
EN: 13. Remember to wear slippers at home and not walk barefoot.

ZH: 14. 记得不要在公共场所大声喧哗。
EN: 14. Remember not to make loud noises in public places.

ZH: 15. 记得在户外活动时擦防晒霜。
EN: 15. Remember to apply sunscreen when engaging in outdoor activities.

ZH: 16. 记得把房间打扫干净才走。
EN: 16. Remember to clean up the room before leaving.

ZH: 17. 记得带上所有必需的文件和证件。
EN: 17. Remember to bring all necessary documents and identification.

ZH: 18. 记得按时交作业，不要迟到。
EN: 18. Remember to submit your homework on time and do not be late.

ZH: 19. 记得在冬天穿厚衣服，不要着凉。
EN: 19. Remember to wear warm clothes in winter and avoid catching a cold.

ZH: 20. 记得要尊重长辈的意见和建议。
EN: 20. Remember to respect the opinions and advice of elders.
